    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Neither Cross Nor Crown is a third person medieval melee combat game similar to the classic Soulslike precursor Severance: Blade of Darkness.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153320/extras/8507b8094054b12c029bf9563a670e67.poster.avif?t=1762177338\" width=700 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153320/extras/8507b8094054b12c029bf9563a670e67.webm?t=1762177338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player can expect:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Weighty combat featuring dismemberment </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ambient environments and extensive exploration </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Five non-linear levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A unique historical fantasy setting based on the German Peasants' War of 1525 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Lots of armor &amp; weapons to customize your character </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A rebellious power fantasy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An original soundtrack by MIDIEvil Studios &amp; featuring a song by Darkrune</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153320/extras/ff0b7d31c985986946bf180b529ff0a0.poster.avif?t=1762177338\" width=700 height=370 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153320/extras/ff0b7d31c985986946bf180b529ff0a0.webm?t=1762177338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
